name: Explora - Travel Tickets Booking App
description: This is Explora, a travel tickets booking app. Available features include: Recommended places, search place, save place, book place, profile, and inbox. I design this with my friend, Aldito. Tools that we use is: Figma, Flaticon, Unsplash, and Dribbble. We made this for about one week. You can criticize our design at the comment section. Thank you!
